{"pageProps":{"path":"lc-maximum-product-subarray","post":{"title":"152. 乘积最大子数组","body":"<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\">\n<div id=\"toctitle\">目录</div>\n<ul class=\"sectlevel1\">\n<li><a href=\"#_利用本题的性质\">利用本题的性质</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#_动态规划\">动态规划</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>题目<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/maximum-product-subarray/\">152. 乘积最大子数组</a>。\n这个题目和<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/maximum-subarray/\">53. 最大子序和</a>不太一样，\n原因是有负数的连乘会导致符号变来变去。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>最开始，除了暴力方法之外，我没啥头绪，看了其他人写的题解，我才找到点感觉。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_利用本题的性质\">利用本题的性质</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>性质一</strong>：在一个不含 0 的数组中，最大乘积不可能是数组的中间某部分。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>证明</strong>：如果最大乘积在数组的中间部分，那么就可以把数组分成前面、中间、后面三部分，其中中间部分的乘积是最大乘积。我们记\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span>、<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">b</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span>、<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span></span></span></span> 分别表示这三部分的乘积，那么</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">b&gt;0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></p>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>如果 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span></span></span></span> 同号，则 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mi>c</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">abc &gt; b</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span>，矛盾；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span></span></span></span> 异号，那么其中一个一定大于零，记 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>max</mtext><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>c</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x = \\textrm{max}(a,c)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord textrm\">max</span></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>，则 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">xb &gt; b</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span>，矛盾。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">b&lt;0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></p>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>如果 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span></span></span></span> 中有一个为负数，记为之 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span>，则 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&gt;</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">xb &gt; 0 &gt; b</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.73354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68354em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span>，矛盾；</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span> 和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span></span></span></span> 都是整数，则它们都大于 0，进而大于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">b</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span>，矛盾。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这就证完了。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这个性质是说，最大乘积要么包含第一个数，要么包含最后一个数。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>性质二</strong>：如果数组长度大于 1，则最大乘积至少是 0。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><strong>证明</strong>：任意选取数组中的连续两数。如果它们之中至少有一个 0，那么数组的最大成绩肯定大于或等于 0。\n如果都不为 0，如果它们同号，那么同号相乘大于 0；如果它们异号，则至少有一个大于 0。证完。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>这个性质可以简化代码。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>沿着性质一的思路，我们只要把数组分成一些连续的、不含 0 的子数组，分别计算最大乘积就好了。代码如下：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">nums</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> maxProduct = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">nums</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (nums.length === <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> nums[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> list = [];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> max = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 根据性质二，结果至少是 0，就初始化为 0 好了</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">of</span> nums) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (n != <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n            list.push(n)\n        } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (list.length &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n                max = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(max, maxProductForNonZeroList(list))\n                list = []\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (list.length &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n        max = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(max, maxProductForNonZeroList(list))\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> max\n};\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">maxProductForNonZeroList</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">nums</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 从左往右算一遍</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> LEN = nums.length;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> base = nums[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> leftMax = nums[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; LEN; i++) {\n        base *= nums[i];\n        leftMax = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(base, leftMax)\n    }\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 从右往左算一遍</span>\n    base = nums[LEN - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> rightMax = nums[LEN - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = LEN - <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>; i &gt;= <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i--) {\n        base *= nums[i];\n        rightMax = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(base, rightMax)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(leftMax, rightMax)\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_动态规划\">动态规划</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>动态规划对我来说比较难想，看懂了就自己说一遍再写一遍吧。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>因为有负数的连乘中，积的符号会变来变去，所以干脆维护两个列表——最大乘积的列表和最小乘积的列表，\n分别记为 <code>maxs</code> 和 <code>mins</code> 吧。<code>maxs[i]</code> 的精确说法是，<code>nums</code> 数组中以 <code>nums[i]</code>\n结尾的连续子数组中最大乘积，<code>mins</code> 类似，不啰嗦了。显然，<code>maxs[0] = nums[0]</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>显然（因为详细说起来太啰嗦了。。），<code>maxs[i] = max(maxs[i-1]*nums[i], mins[i-1]*nums[i])</code>。如果\n<code>mins[i-1]</code> 和 <code>maxs[i-1]</code> 都是 0，显然 <code>maxs[i] = nums[i]</code>。这样，公式就可以这么写：\n<code>maxs[i] = max(maxs[i-1]*nums[i], mins[i-1]*nums[i], nums[i])</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p><code>mins[i]</code> 的递推公式类似。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>于是可以写出下面的代码：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-js\" data-lang=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@param <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number[]}</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">nums</span></span>\n * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return <span class=\"hljs-type\">{number}</span></span>\n */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> maxProduct = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">nums</span>) </span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> mins = [nums[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]], maxs = [nums[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>]];\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt; nums.length; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> n = nums[i];\n        mins[i] = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.min(mins[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] * n, maxs[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] * n, n);\n        maxs[i] = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(mins[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] * n, maxs[i - <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] * n, n);\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Math</span>.max(...maxs)\n};</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>从公式中看，数组 <code>mins</code> 和 <code>maxs</code> 是可以被优化掉，从而达到仅使用 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(1)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 的额外空间这种境界。\n优化方式比较简单，算了。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","createTime":1611072000000,"authorName":"weily","type":"adoc"}},"__N_SSG":true}